com.simiacryptus.mindseye.layers.cudnn

Class ProductLayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang.NNLayer
      • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.layers.cudnn.ProductLayer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LayerPrecision<ProductLayer>, Serializable

    public class ProductLayer
extends NNLayer
implements LayerPrecision<ProductLayer>
    This layer multiplies together the inputs, element-by-element. It can be used to implement integer-power activation layers, such as the square needed in MeanSqLossLayer.
